<p><a href="https://www.dooza.ai/workflow"><strong>Dooza Workflow</strong></a> takes a different approach. It is a done-for-you AI employee platform — meaning you get a pre-built AI worker that handles lead follow-up from day one. No sequence building. No template writing. No integration headaches.</p>
