<p>At <strong>$199 per month</strong>, it costs a fraction of what you would pay for a human SDR ($4,000-$5,000/month), a virtual assistant ($2,000-$3,000/month), or even a BPO arrangement. And unlike a human hire, it works 24/7 without sick days, training ramps, or inconsistent performance.</p>
